OL,3,COne in six beds left vacant in some
OL,4,Cprivate Guernsey care homes
OL,6,FOne in six beds in some of 's private
OL,7,Fcare homes are not being used.
OL,9,FIt is thought that despite high
OL,10,Fdemand, there are 40 empty rooms
OL,11,Facross the island.
OL,13,FCare home owner Martin Joyce says the
OL,14,Fissue is a backlog with the Needs
OL,15,FAssessment Panel (NAPS), which decides
OL,16,Fon the type of care best suited to
OL,17,Fsomeone's needs.
OL,19,FMartin explains that some people stay
OL,20,Fin hospital for months while they wait
OL,21,Ffor their needs to be met.
