OL,6,FHe adds: "What we're trying to urge
OL,7,Fthe authorities to do is make an
OL,8,Fadditional category which would be to
OL,9,Fgive interim care to those who would
OL,10,Fotherwise be waiting in hospital for a
OL,11,Fhome package.
OL,13,F"There's somebody in a hospital bed at
OL,14,Fpresent, who has waited for six
OL,15,Fmonths."
OL,17,FOne Guernsey resident says the empty
OL,18,Fcare home rooms are simply because
OL,19,Fbeds are too expensive.
