OL,4,Cprivate Guernsey care homes
OL,6,F"That's the difficulty, we might have
OL,7,Fto fork out for five or 10 years."
OL,9,FThe States of Guernsey offers help for
OL,10,Fprivate care, with #609 a week for
OL,11,Fresidential homes.
OL,13,FEveryone has to pay #327.32 weekly
OL,14,Ffrom individual pensions or assets - a
OL,15,Fflat fee that is not means-tested.
