OL,3,COne in six beds left vacant in some
OL,4,Cprivate Guernsey care homes
OL,6,FChair of CareWatch, Bella Farrell,
OL,7,Fsays: "There are lots of issues but
OL,8,Ffair access is one. It's very hard for
OL,9,Fme to think you might have a lot of
OL,10,Fassets and yet you would not pay fully
OL,11,Ffor your care later on in life.
OL,13,F"Equally, if you don't have those
OL,14,Fassets. I can see why people would
OL,15,Fthink I've worked all these years for
OL,16,Fmy home and now I have to sell it for
OL,17,Fmy care and that's tough for people
OL,18,Ftoo."
